{"tid":2076560,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"習總又犯規? 錢其琛: 中共拯救香港股市, 是違反「一國兩制」","createTime":"2020-06-23T15:16:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T15:31:01.000Z","uid":134071,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9d3d5166bbb9dda7a4e16b9b4dd8c5e4e2f5c88d","tid":2076560,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T15:16:04.000Z","msg":"而家, 習總不斷叫中概股拯救香港股市, 為證明國安法唔會破壞香港經濟.<br />\n<br />\n但根據 錢其琛所言, 佢係犯規<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em>全國政協副主席、前行政長官董建華表示，<strong>1998年特區政府入市打擊炒家前，曾致電時任國務院副總理錢其琛，詢問中央是否要人來港協助，錢其琛思考後拒絕，認為不符合一國兩制。</strong><br />\n.............<br />\n董引述錢其琛說，中央對港府有信心，相信港府能解決困難。董笑言，是錢其琛提醒他一國兩制下中央不干預香港事務，<strong>董再引述錢說：「在一國兩制下，我們（中央）不應派人來港，你不記得嗎？」</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20170707/s00001/1499416884207\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170707%2Fs00001%2F1499416884207&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JS8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=b651ccc6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170707%2Fs00001%2F1499416884207&h=4820e0b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20170707/s00001/1499416884207</a>"},{"pid":"ff208931096814274cf88fbf97bdfbebe5895dae","tid":2076560,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T15:17:07.000Z","msg":"反而, 雜種就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中概股回歸引爆吸資潮 香港危轉機保金融地位<br />\n2020-06-22<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E4%B8%AD%E6%A6%82%E8%82%A1%E5%9B%9E%E6%AD%B8%E5%BC%95%E7%88%86%E5%90%B8%E8%B3%87%E6%BD%AE-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%B1%E8%BD%89%E6%A9%9F%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E5%9C%B0%E4%BD%8D-22376